Problem:
---------
Letâ€™s group magazines according to category and rank each group in descending order by price. Display the ranking position, name, category, and price for each magazine.

Solution
--------
SELECT
  category,
  name,
  price,
  RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY category
                    ORDER BY price DESC
                    ) AS price_rank
FROM magazine;


References:
    1. https://learnsql.com/cookbook/how-to-rank-rows-within-a-partition-in-sql/
    2. https://www.sqlshack.com/overview-of-sql-rank-functions/